name: Montaneza Falls (Cebu Philippines)
description:
Introduction

A fun run in south/west Cebu with some nice drops and a few jumps.

Approach

Hike the road to the jump-off point then up a trail to the drop-in.

Descent

All anchors are in place and solid. The action starts pretty quick once your in the watercourse with a big drop down into a gorge followed by a handful of raps and jumps before reaching a hot springs.

Exit

Exit the river heading west near the hot springs through a village to the road and your ride.
